OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry with variable cloud
OL,6,Famounts. Some sunny spells are likely,
OL,7,Fwith temperatures near normal for
OL,8,FMarch, however the breeze will lead to
OL,9,Fit feeling cooler. Although the odd
OL,10,Fshower cannot be ruled out, mainly
OL,11,Fduring the morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud thickening through the
OL,14,Fevening and overnight. Winds also
OL,15,Fstrengthening, with upland gales
OL,16,Flikely, and perhaps some rain for a
OL,17,Ftime. Likely staying frost free.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
